---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', item: '/' },
  { name: 'About Us', item: '/about' }
];
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Us - CreatorsFeel"
  description="Discover the mission behind CreatorsFeel. Learn why we build premium, free, privacy-first marketing and analytics tools for social media creators."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
  <article class="info-page container">
    <header class="info-header text-center">
      <h1 class="info-title">About CreatorsFeel</h1>
      <p class="info-subtitle text-muted">Building the ultimate optimization engine for digital content creators.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="info-content glass">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        CreatorsFeel was founded with a single, clear objective: **to democratize creator metrics**. Navigating sponsorship negotiations, audience engagement formulas, and title SEO copywriting can be intimidating for creators starting out.
      </p>
      <p>
        Most marketing dashboards are hidden behind expensive subscriptions, bloated ads, or data-collection tracking. We built CreatorsFeel to deliver **premium, 100% free, and privacy-first analytics tools** that load instantly.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Performance First</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">No lag, loaders, or loading screens. Our tools compile to static assets and run calculations instantly inside your browser.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" /></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Uncompromised Privacy</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">We do not store, log, or sell your account figures. All calculator metrics are processed locally. Your account data stays yours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" /></svg>
          </span>
          <h3>Premium Quality</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">AdSense-friendly, clean layouts optimized for both light and dark systems. We avoid distracting banners and invasive grids.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Our Current Suite</h2>
      <p>
        We launched with three primary optimization tools designed to solve daily creator bottlenecks:
      </p>
      <ul class="tools-list">
        <li><strong>Influencer Rate Calculator:</strong> Estimate sponsored post rate baselines and export customized copy-paste pitch templates.</li>
        <li><strong>Instagram Engagement Calculator:</strong> Audit followers, comment ratios, and evaluate account interaction tiers.</li>
        <li><strong>YouTube Title Checker:</strong> Run real-time character limit counts, scan for emotional power words, and preview layouts.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>A Future-Proof Platform</h2>
      <p>
        This is just the beginning. Our architecture is designed to scale to **hundreds of specialized creator tools** covering TikTok algorithms, Twitch viewer analytics, podcast layouts, script templates, and invoice generators. 
      </p>
      <p>
        Have ideas or feedback? Let us know on our <a href="/contact" class="info-link">Contact Page</a>!
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .info-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    padding-top: var(--space-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .info-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .info-title {
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .info-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }

  .info-content {
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .info-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .info-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .info-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .tools-list {
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .tools-list strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* Values grid */
  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .value-item {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--gradient-glow);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    color: var(--color-brand);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .value-icon :global(svg) {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .value-item p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .info-link {
    color: var(--color-brand);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .info-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* Responsive Rules */
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
